  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of middle years, marked by taupe skin and the dense forearm musculature typical of repeated heavy lifting. Brown eyes sit beneath straight brows, set in a square face with a notably broken nose that has healed slightly off-center. Brown hair is kept in a short, practical cut that leaves the ears clear and the nape exposed. The hands present thickened knuckles and old burn-speckling along the fingers, permanent traces of long service behind a working bar.",
